Body: Description: Hi Team, We are facing some issues with the reports, there's this error where the system error is showing 'Unexpected exception: Encountered Error: 'Reports.xml has not been transformed at drive: " while generating report Kindly assign someone to troubleshoot this with us on this, thank you.
What We've Learned Updated: APAC timezone

What We've Learned Updated: When we clicked on reports, we saw this error message:

'Unexpected exception: Encountered error: Reports.xml has not been transformed at F:Program FilesSTEALTHbitsStealthAUDITReports."


To resolve this issue, we navigated to the above directory, made a backup of reports.xml and then deleted the file from parent folder. After that we re-launched the NEA console, and we were able to view reports.
Next Steps Updated: Customer will update us by end of the day. I will follow up with them next week if no response received.
